Unknown gunmen, on Sunday, attacked worshippers at St. Moses Catholic Church in Robuh, Unguwan Aku, Kajuru LGA of Kaduna State while winding down their first mass.
It gathered that the gunmen came to the church in large numbers and started shooting sporadically at the worshippers.
In the course of the attack on the church, three worshippers were killed, some kidnapped while others sustained varying degree of injuries
One of the victims of the attack, according to reports, was brought to St. Gerard Catholic Hospital, Kaduna for medical attention.
